                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 774/707.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">de Billier</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-03-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 21, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. de Billier says a delegate will be sent to the opium conference by the
                    Government of Persia.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
